<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Imgur Gallery</title><link>https://imgur.com</link><description>description</description><lastBuildDate>2022-05-11 22:13:05.705551</lastBuildDate><item><title>I have been keeping a secret</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/zKmH6tA</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PWsy759.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My family is going through a lot individually and I've been very mum about this struggle I've been going through.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/p3oncKw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>In vague terms, I've been "high risk" for irregular cell growth and cancer, so I've been dealing with invasive biopsies and screenings for a long time.
But my screening this week came back fully negative for all risk factors.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wCXhsO2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I sound ignorant but I'm trying to live in this joy for a little bit.
Nobody cares, so into the meme void it goes.
Here is my perfectly cat shaped girl.

Edit: My family was made aware of it mostly at large due to things advancing 3 years ago. I just haven't been updating these post screenings. I have another exam in 6 months and if I still stay clear it gets to go down to once a year, so we're still staying diligent.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/zKmH6tA</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CakesAndClowns]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>:)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/EGDiGGu</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HhDxFRH.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/EGDiGGu</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[duckbutter888]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>#TIL they are really PROUD of their incest.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/bhyUPvL</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tJebt34.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/bhyUPvL</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[sleeperkid]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>She has a heartbeat too</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/xLsOAjp</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vixRsjz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fJToe6y.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IA1KYQN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5IQUasx.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Viral edit: please read, this is why I chose this title

